spec_data.Name: php-psr-cache
spec_data.Description:
This package holds all interfaces defined by PSR-6 [1].

Note that this is not a Cache implementation of its own. It is merely an
interface that describes a Cache implementation. See the specification for
more details.

Autoloader: /usr/share/php/Psr/Cache/autoload.php

[1] http://www.php-fig.org/psr/psr-6/
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 09:07:24 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: PSR Cache: Common interface for caching libraries
